    #1, b\xE1o c\xE1o th\xED nghi\u1EC7m ho\xE0n ch\u1EC9nh #1). Nh\u1EA5n E \u0111\u1EC3
    t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c v\u1EDBi th\xF9ng loot. C\xF3 th\u1EC3 ho\xE0n th\xE0nh
    b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch thu th\u1EADp \u0111\u1EE7 t\xE0i li\u1EC7u ho\u1EB7c t\u01B0\u01A1ng
    t\xE1c th\xF9ng loot."
  objective: "Thu th\u1EADp 4 t\xE0i li\u1EC7u trong c\xF4ng tr\u01B0\u1EDDng HO\u1EB6C
    loot th\xF9ng v\u1EADt t\u01B0"
